I have this code
``` python
def spread(arg):
    ret = []
    for i in arg:
        if isinstance(i, list):
            ret.extend(i)
        else:
            ret.append(i)
    return ret

 def deep_flatten(arr):
    result = []
    result.extend(spread(list(map(lambda x : deep(x) if type(x) == list else x,arr))))
    return result
```

I run auto-pep8 and I get this
```py



