The generic HMDevice could make use of these functions, especially to retrieve device names, but maybe also other data.

```
input_model = api.model('TransformInput', {
    'feed_name': fields.String(description='Feed name.'),
    'raw_data': fields.String(description='Raw XML content.', required=True),
    'meta': fields.Raw(description='Associated metadata.')
})

class TransformResource(Resource):
    @api.expect(input_model)
    def get(self):
        data = request.json # Exception here because request.data is empty.
        return None, 204
```

